@0 = ~Greetings! I am Arto, a Red Wizard of Thay. I have numerous arcane and magical items that I would be pleased to sell to you at semi-reasonable prices.~
@1 = ~Let me see what you have.~
@2 = ~Who are the Red Wizards?~
@3 = ~Goodbye.~
@4 = ~Be sure that you purchase something. I prefer not to display my wares for oglers and rubber-neckers.~
@5 = ~The Red Wizards are the masters of all that is arcane. We have enclaves throughout the Realms where we offer a variety of magical exports from Thay. I am one such merchant and member.~
@6 = ~So this is your enclave? Impressive. No, really.~
@7 = ~This you enclave? It pretty pathetic.~
@8 = ~Yes, come again.~
@9 = ~MT: Это НЕ мой анклав, ты, лысая обезьяна. Я здесь по необходимости. Мой анклав был уничтожен Высшими Капитанами, как и большая часть города. Когда все успокоится, я вернусь. Ну так как, хотите вы что-нибудь купить, или нет?~ /*This is NOT my enclave, you hairless monkey. I am here from necessity. My enclave was destroyed by the High Captains, like much of this city. Once things calm down I will return.*/
